ysia (since 2011)\n* {{flagicon|MYS}} '''[[Petaling Jaya]]''', Malaysia (since 2012)\n* {{flagicon|MAR}} '''[[Rabat]]''', Morocco (since 2013)\n* {{flagicon|VNM}} '''[[B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng Province]]''', Vietnam (since 2013)\n* {{flagicon|IND}} '''[[Ahmedabad]]''', India (since 2014)\n* {{flagicon|POL}} '''[[\u0141\u00f3d\u017a]]''', Poland (since 2014)\n* {{flagicon|BAN}} '''[[Dhaka]]''', Bangladesh\n* {{flagicon|MEX}} '''[[Ecatepec]]''', Mexico (since 2016)<ref>{{cite web |title=Gestiona Ecatepec oportunidades para intercambios estudiantiles con Guangzhou, China |url=http://diarioportal.com/post/141160145154/gestiona-ecatepec-oportunidades-para-intercambios |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323083435/http://diarioportal.com/post/141160145154/gestiona-ecatepec-oportunidades-para-intercambios |archive-date=2016-03-23 |access-date=2017-12-30 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Relaci\u00f3n M\u00e9xico-Estados Unidos necesita puentes para construir paz, respeto y reconocimiento, no muros: EAV |url=http://diarioportal.com/post/140999609764/relaci\u00f3n-m\u00e9xico-estados-unidos-necesita-puentes#x |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170905151736/http://diarioportal.com/post/140999609764/relaci%C3%B3n-m%C3%A9xico-estados-unidos-necesita-puentes#x |archive-date=2017-09-05 |access-date=2018-04-02 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Viajar\u00e1n a China alumnos de Ecatepec |url=http://www.hoyestado.com/2016/03/viajaran-a-china-alumnos-de-ecatepec |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160411091125/http://www.hoyestado.com/2016/03/viajaran-a-china-alumnos-de-ecatepec/ |archive-date=2016-04-11 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Gestiona Ecatepec oportunidades para Intercambios estudiantiles con Guangzhou, China |url=http://www.edomexaldia.com.mx/2016/03/gestiona-ecatepec-oportunidades-para-intercambios-estudiantiles-con-guangzhou-china/ |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170905053320